text: Leif Larsson (9 August 1928 - 11 February 2002) was a Swedish sports shooter. He competed at the 1960, 1964 and 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:2002 deaths Category:Swedish male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Sweden Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Gothenburg
